The city has held the 2005 NCAA Men 's Basketball First and Second round and hosted the Big 12 Men 's and Women 's Basketball Tournaments in 2007 and 2009 .
The major universities in the area -- University of Oklahoma , Oklahoma City University , and Oklahoma State University -- often schedule major basketball games and other sporting events at Chesapeake Energy Arena and Chickasaw Bricktown Ballpark , although most home games are played at their campus stadiums .
There are numerous golf courses and country clubs spread around the city .
The state of Oklahoma hosts a highly competitive high school football culture , with many teams in the Oklahoma City metropolitan area .
Beginning with the largest , the classes are : 6A , 5A , 4A , 3A , 2A , A , B , and C. Class 6A is broken into two divisions .
Oklahoma City area schools in this division include : Edmond North , Mustang , Moore , Yukon , Edmond Memorial , Edmond Santa Fe , Norman North , Westmoore , Southmoore , Putnam City North , Norman , Putnam City , Putnam City West , U.S. Grant , Midwest City .
The Thunder plays home games at the Chesapeake Energy Arena in downtown Oklahoma City , known affectionately in the national media as ` the Peake ' and ` Loud City ' .
In 2013 the Thunder reached the Western Conference semifinals without All-Star guard Russell Westbrook , who was injured in their first round series against the Houston Rockets , only to lose to the Memphis Grizzlies .
The Oklahoma City Thunder has been regarded by sports analysts as one of the elite franchises of the NBA 's Western Conference and that of a media darling as the future of the league .
The team became the first NBA franchise to play regular-season games in the state of Oklahoma .
-LSB- citation needed -RSB- The team was known as the New Orleans/Oklahoma City Hornets while playing in Oklahoma City .
