The club was promoted back to the Premier League in 2012 following a brief spell in the third-tier and severe financial difficulties .
In 2015 , `` The Saints '' finished 7th in the Premier League , their highest league finish in 30 years , after a remarkable season under new manager Ronald Koeman .
Their highest league position came in 1984 when they were runners-up in the old First Division .
They were also runners-up in the 1979 Football League Cup final and 2003 FA Cup final .
