The town of his parish was renamed Dolores Hidalgo in his honor and the state of Hidalgo was created in 1869 .
Every year on the night of 15 -- 16 September , the president of Mexico re-enacts the Grito from the balcony of the National Palace .
This scene is repeated by the heads of cities and towns all over Mexico .
Next to it is a lamp lit to represent the sacrifice of those who gave their lives for Mexican Independence .
