Journey released their eponymous debut in 1975 and the next year Boston released their highly successful début album .
In the same year , hard rock bands featuring women saw commercial success as Heart released Dreamboat Annie and The Runaways débuted with their self-titled album .
While Heart had a more folk-oriented hard rock sound , the Runaways leaned more towards a mix of punk-influenced music and hard rock .
