It has settled a dispute with Richard Jewell , who was a private security guard at the venue , along with some media organizations , in regard to the leaking of his name during the investigation .
The book suggested that the FBI has not evolved into an effective counter-terrorism or counter-intelligence agency , due in large part to deeply ingrained agency cultural resistance to change .
For example , FBI personnel practices continue to treat all staff other than special agents as support staff , classifying intelligence analysts alongside the FBI 's auto mechanics and janitors .
The lab serves as the primary lab for most DNA , biological , and physical work .
