Melbourne is Australia 's second-largest industrial centre .
It is the Australian base for a number of significant manufacturers including Boeing , truck-makers Kenworth and Iveco , Cadbury as well as Bombardier Transportation and Jayco , among many others .
It is also home to a wide variety of other manufacturers , ranging from petrochemicals and pharmaceuticals to fashion garments , paper manufacturing and food processing .
