Al-Harizi compared Saladin 's decree allowing Jews to re-establish themselves in Jerusalem to the one issued by the Persian king Cyrus the Great over 1,600 years earlier .
Jerusalem , although left without the protection of any city walls since 1219 , also saw a flurry of new construction projects centred around the Al-Aqsa Mosque compound -LRB- the Temple Mount -RRB- .
