White Americans of all European backgrounds are present in all areas of the state .
Those of English and Irish ancestry are present in large numbers in all the urban/suburban areas across the state .
Florida 's Hispanic population includes large communities of Cuban Americans in Miami and Tampa , Puerto Ricans in Orlando and Tampa , and Mexican/Central American migrant workers .
The Hispanic community continues to grow more affluent and mobile .
As of 2011 , 57.0 % of Florida 's children under the age of 1 belonged to minority groups .
Florida has a large and diverse Hispanic population , with Cubans and Puerto Ricans being the largest groups in the state .
Puerto Ricans are more widespread throughout the state , though the heaviest concentrations are in the Orlando area of Central Florida .
