`` Bohemian Rhapsody '' was re-released as a single shortly after Mercury 's death , with `` These Are the Days of Our Lives '' as the double A-side .
The single went to number one in the UK , remaining there for five weeks -- the only recording to top the Christmas chart twice and the only one to be number one in four different years -LRB- 1975 , 1976 , 1991 , and 1992 -RRB- .
