The responses to Madonna 's excessively provocative videos have been predictably contradictory . ''
The media and public reaction towards her most-discussed songs such as `` Papa Do n't Preach '' , `` Like a Prayer '' , or `` Justify My Love '' had to do with the music videos created to promote the songs and their impact , rather than the songs themselves .
