He is buried beneath the floor of Saint Peter 's Basilica with other popes .
In his will , he requested to be buried in the `` true earth '' and therefore , he does not have an ornate sarcophagus but an in-ground grave .
With the six consistories , Paul VI continued the internationalization policies started by Pius XII in 1946 and continued by John XXIII .
