-LSB- citation needed -RSB- Globalization in this context can be defined as western civilization in other ways , it undermines the cultural integrity of other culture and it is therefore repressive , exploitative and harmful to most people in different places .
-LSB- citation needed -RSB- Similarly , the discipline widens the concept of `` culture '' .
The last two , in fact , have become the main focus of cultural studies .
