-LRB- Harmonised Index of Consumer Prices -RRB- Unlike for example the United States Federal Reserve Bank , the ECB has only one primary objective but this objective has never been defined in statutory law , and the HICP target can be termed ad-hoc .
The banks in effect borrow cash and must pay it back ; the short durations allow interest rates to be adjusted continually .
When the repo notes come due the participating banks bid again .
