Guamanians are American citizens by birth .
Guam has an area of 544 km2 -LRB- 210 sq mi -RRB- and a density of 297/km ² -LRB- 770/sq mi -RRB- .
It is the largest and southernmost of the Mariana Islands , and the largest island in Micronesia .
Among its municipalities , Mongmong-Toto-Maite has the highest density at 1,425 / km ² -LRB- 3,691 / sq mi -RRB- , whereas Inarajan and Umatac have the lowest density at 47/km ² -LRB- 119/sq mi -RRB- .
Between the 1500s and the 1700s , Guam was an important stopover for the Spanish Manila Galleons .
During the Spanish -- American War , the United States captured Guam on June 21 , 1898 .
Guam is amongst the seventeen Non-Self-Governing Territories of the United Nations .
During the occupation , Guamanians were subjected to culture alignment , forced labor , beheadings , rape , and torture .
Guam endured hostilities when American forces recaptured the island on July 21 , 1944 ; Liberation Day commemorates the victory .
Since the 1960s , the economy is supported by two industries : tourism and the United States Armed Forces .
