The northeast end is dotted with residential areas .
The Charminar , Mecca Masjid , Charkaman and Qutb Shahi tombs are other existing structures of this period .
Most of the historical bazaars that still exist were constructed on the street north of Charminar towards Golconda fort .
During Mir Osman Ali Khan 's rule , European styles , along with Indo-Islamic , became prominent .
