Today religion and politics continues to thrive in the Commonwealth of Virginia .
In addition , there are several Technical Colleges in Richmond including ITT Technical Institute , ECPI College of Technology and Centura College .
There are several vocational colleges also , such as Fortis College and Bryant Stratton College .
