Some California and Southwestern tribes , such as the Kumeyaay , Cocopa , Pascua Yaqui and Apache span both sides of the US -- Mexican border .
Athabascan , Tlingit , Haida , Tsimshian , Iñupiat , Blackfeet , Nakota , Cree , Anishinaabe , Huron , Lenape , Mi ` kmaq , Penobscot , and Haudenosaunee , among others live in both Canada and the US .
